Number Pattern 2
Send Feedback
Print the following pattern
Pattern for N = 4


The dots represent spaces.



Input Format :
N (Total no. of rows)
Output Format :
Pattern in N lines
Sample Input :
5
Sample Output :


The dots represent spaces.








#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    int i=1;
    while(i<=n){
        int j=1;
        int k=i;
        int space=n-i;
        while(space>=1){
            cout<<" ";
            space--;
        }
        while(j<=i){
            cout<<k;
            j++;
            k++;
        }
        cout<<endl;
        i++;
    }
}
